parameters:
Ugh, you're kidding, right...? Are you saying that all of my
magic is unnecessary...?

\SE[7]W-Well, it's not like it's completely unnecessary... but if
it's just \SE[21]that much, you could just make it yourself...

If it's just 'that much'...!? The magic of the spirits... if it's
just 'that much'...!?

\SE[92]Huh? Even though you're a spirit, you can't grant me any
power? \SE[29]I came all the way to this place, so it's the worst
if it ends up being a wasted trip, you know?
I'm trying my best to think right now...!! Don't interrupt me!!
Ouch...! The wound inflicted by that woman hurts...

\SE[2]A-Are you okay...? I-If it seems too difficult, i-it's okay
even if you can't give me any power or anything...
Ugh... As a spirit, I can't just...! Wait... Wound... Sword...?!
Lunaroa! Are you perhaps... struggling with choosing a weapon?!

\SE[2]Ah... Indeed, that might be true... \!\SE[1]It's not easy
to find a weapon that can do both physical and magic...

Alright! Then I'll give you a weapon blessed with my protection!
You should be satisfied with that...! How about it...!?

A weapon of the spirits!! Don't say things like with that! Don't
interrupt me...! It's an amazing thing...!
\SE[21]Wow...! I'm really looking forward to it...!

Huh... It's really amazing...!? You'll definitely be surprised if
you see it...!! ...Argh!

Lunaroa obtained the Blade of Zero Flowers! She learned the
secret technique Zero Flowers: Misty Flash!
\SE[1]Ah... I seem to have received a lot.

Sorry for keeping you waiting... My service to you... My
service...

Hehehe... That secret technique is, you know... a technique that
steals her identity...!
\SE[102]Are you referring to me when you say that woman...?

Listen and be amazed!! That secret technique doesn't consume any
turns when used! I completely nullified your individuality...!

How about it? Isn't it frustrating...? This is something you have
to admit as a loss, right?

\SE\SE[0]... Huh? So, does that mean Laura and I will be
matching? \SE[16] Yay! \SE[0] I noticed that Laura was having fun
zooming around, so I thought it would be nice to join in. Now we
can zoom around together.

\SE\SE[21]Well then, we're done here, right? Let's hurry back
from this place and go eat dessert at Ulyssean.

\SE\SE[0]Vita. It's over. It's about time to go home. \SE[0]Oh, I
also need to wake up Vega...

\SE[14]Hmm... I understand... \SE[15]Just a little more, because
it's a nice round number... After it's over...
